Package: RobustIV
Type: Package
Title: Robust Inference for Causal Effect with Possibly Invalid Instrumental Variables
Version: 0.2.2
Author: Taehyeon Koo, Zhenyu Wang, Sai Li, Hyunseung Kang, Zijian Guo   
Maintainer: Zijian Guo <zijguo@stat.rutgers.edu>
Description: This package provides functions for robust inference in the presence of potentially invalid instrumental variables, including TSHT method, Searching and Sampling, and SpotIV method. It also provides inference for non-linear outcome models with the control function method and conduct the endogeneity test in high dimensions. 
License: GPL-3
